ActCanada Student Financial Assistance Act
SubjectAdministrative Fees - Agreements
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development enter into AGREEMENTS or ARRANGEMENTS with the governments of the provinces participating under the Canada Student Financial Assistance Act for the purpose of providing for administrative fees in compensation for services rendered on behalf of the federal government.
